          "Muhammad Bin Yahya, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Ali Bin Al Noman, from Abu Al Sabbah Al Kanany who said, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘The one who harms with something from the roads of the Muslims, so he is responsible for it’."
